ned a deserved award &quot;World Finance Banking Awards&quot;, an annual award given by the British magazine World Finance, specializing in financial journalism and business.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>','BOI Bank Corporation',1,'About the bank',1,2,1,NULL),(138,NULL,'<div>\r\n	<strong>Street Address:</strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Walk Village Commercial Center,</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Suite # 206, 1st Floor,</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Friar\'s Hill Road, St.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	John\'s Antigua</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong>Phone:</strong> 1 268 5624471</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong>Fax:</strong> 1 268 5624470</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong>Web:</strong> www.boibank.com</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong>Message:</strong>&nbsp;info@BOIbank.co</div>',NULL,1,'Where we are',1,2,1,NULL),(139,NULL,'<div>\r\n	<strong>Products for liquidity management</strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong>Benefits:</strong></div>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Attractive interest rates according to the amount of their investment.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Access to System consultation and online transactions through www.boibank.com.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Sending transfers in and out of the United States in the currency you want.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong>Investment Products</strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong>Certificates of deposit</strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	The deposits of BOI Bank provide an opportunity to secure investment with attractive returns.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong>Benefits:</strong></div>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Attractive interest rate, with interest payments as agreed within your investment (for