ernet browser, which will get safety improvements include manufacturers constantly.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Create passwords difficult to guess.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Our recommendation is to create combinations of uppercase, lowercase, numbers and special characters.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Do not use data such as names of relatives, birth dates, etc.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Make sure you have installed and updated antivirus software.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Install a personal firewall, which will help prevent unauthorized access of third parties to your computer.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Do not deviate from your computer when you are making transactions on your internet banking.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<strong>Protect your Computer</strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Misuse of Internet increases the chance of infection by computer virus programs and infiltration by intrusion.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;Computer viruses can modify programs and delete files on your machine; intrusion programs can cause similar effects, and are able to record the keys you press in order to obtain confidential information.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	We recommend that you follow these practices:</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Use a firewall, which is a piece of hardware or software that helps prevent intruders or viruses from entering your machine.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Update the software on your computer. If you are using any Windows programs, install the latest security releases.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Install an antivirus, which is a program that helps you keep your machine protected against computer viruses, Trojan horses, and other unwanted intruders.</li>\r\n</ul>','',1,'Safety tips',1,2,1,'icono_tips-seguridad.jpg'),(149,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'NUESTRO BANCO',1,1,1,NULL),(150,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'PRODUCTOS',1,1,1,NULL),(151,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'UBÍQUENOS',1,1,1,NULL),(152,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'AYUDA',1,1,1,NULL),(153,N